# ✨ NoteUniv: Python

> #### NoteUniv Python is a script to fetch PDF data from seafile and send them to a database.

<p align="center"><img src="https://quentium.fr/+img/github/NoteUniv-Python.png"></p>

## 📥 Installation

-   Download the source code [here](https://github.com/NoteUniv/NoteUniv-Python/archive/master.zip) and install the dependencies.

`pip install --upgrade requests python-dotenv pdfminer mysql.connector`

## 🚀 Usage

**WINDOWS & LINUX:**

Rename the .env.example to .env and edit with your constants / tokens.

Simply click twice on `retrieve_mark.py` or run using IDLE / any IDE.

```bash
python retrieve_mark.py
python3 retrieve_mark.py
```
